Smart Environment Monitor - ESP32 Version

Overview

This project is based on ESP32 and is designed to monitor environmental conditions in real time. It displays temperature, humidity, and light intensity while providing visual and audible alerts.

Components Used

- ESP32 DevKit V1
- DHT22 Sensor
- 16x2 I2C LCD Display
- SSD1306 OLED Display
- RGB LED
- Buzzer
- Servo Motor
- LDR Sensor

Features

- Real-time Temperature Monitoring
- Humidity Monitoring
- Light Intensity Detection
- LCD and OLED Display Output
- RGB LED Status Indication
- Buzzer Alert System
- Automatic Servo Motor Control
- Serial Monitor Output

Platform

- Wokwi Simulator
- Arduino IDE

